AMAROK LIVE
===========

ABOUT
-----
This script lets you create your own amaroK live! cd with music on it. It is very simple to use: click configure, and follow the instructions. When it is done, you can add music to the cd by selecting tracks and using the right click menu.

When you are done selecting tracks, click Create Remastered CD. the iso will be created in the work dir that you selected during configure.

DEPENDENCIES
------------
A kernel with squashfs as either a module or compiled in
Python 2.2
PyQt
1.5 gb of free space
Original amaroK live! iso

